    <h1><font face="DFKai-SB">基础概念</font></h1>

    <h2><font face="DFKai-SB">電勢差分佈</font><font face="Segoe Script">（potential different）</font></h2>
    <pre><p><font face="Segoe Script">PN-junction</font></p></pre>
    $$numberof\ electron\ for\ negative\ carries\ is\ N_{n}\\
numberof\ holes\ for\ postive\ carries\ is\ N_{p}\\
P-type\ material\ with\ N_{p}>N_{n}\\
N-type\ material\ with\ N_{n}>N_{p}\\
the\ potential\ of\ N-type\ material\ is\ higher\ then\ P-type\ material\ by\ V\\$$
<pre><p><font face="Segoe Script">by Boltzmann factor</font></p></pre>
$$\frac{N_{i}}{N}=Ae^{-\frac{\varepsilon i}{k_{B}T}}\\
\frac{N_{j}}{N}=Ae^{-\frac{\varepsilon j}{k_{B}T}}\\
\frac{N_{i}}{N_{j}}=e^{-\frac{\varepsilon i-\varepsilon j}{k_{B}T}}\\
=e^{-\frac{q_{ij}V_{ij}}{k_{B}T}}\\
\frac{N_{n}\left ( n-side \right )}{N_{n}\left ( p-side \right )}=e^{-\frac{q_{n}V}{k_{B}T}}\\
\frac{N_{p}\left ( n-side \right )}{N_{p}\left ( p-side \right )}=e^{-\frac{q_{p}V}{k_{B}T}}\\$$
<pre><p><font face="Segoe Script">current</font></p></pre>
$$I_{0}\propto N_{n}\left ( n-side \right )=N_{n}\left ( p-side \right )e^{-\frac{q_{n}V}{k_{B}T}}$$
<pre><p><font face="Segoe Script">external potential </font></p></pre>
    $$I_{1}\propto =N_{n}\left ( p-side \right )e^{-\frac{q_{n}\left (V-\Delta V  \right )}{k_{B}T}} \\
     I_{1}=I_{0}e^{\frac{+q\left (\Delta V  \right )}{k_{B}T}}$$
